40|$|We {{examined}} numerically {{the contribution}} of contrasting characteristics of metal nanoparticles, strong polarization and metallic loss, to the total efficiency of photovoltaic cells. A layer of nanoparticle array was chosen as a model. We found that depending on {{the location of the}} layer in the cell, the metallic <b>loss</b> <b>offsets</b> the enhanced photoabsorption due to the strong near field. A general procedure to reduce a nanoparticle layer into a sheet of effective continuous medium is presented, which greatly facilitates the quantitative analysis...|$|R
